metadata/org.jline/jline-console/index.json:9:    "description" : "JLine Console provides higher-level console framework APIs for building interactive command-line applications on top of JLine. It includes command registry, console engine, system registry, printer, widget, and built-in command support for managing command execution, scripting, completion, and terminal output.",
